<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Covenant_theology&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Advocates">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Advocates</span></h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/John_Ball_(Puritan)" title="John Ball (Puritan)">Ball, John</a> (1645). <i>A Treatise of the Covenant of Grace</i>. Facsimile reprint: Dingwall, Peter and Rachel Reynolds (2006), <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1846852781" class="internal">ISBN 1-84685-278-1</a></li>
